  "remarks": "Subordinate to Shahid Ahmad Kazemi Industries Group (formally the Air\nDefense Missile Industries Group) of Iran's Aerospace Industries Organization (AIO). AIO\ncontrols the missile organizations Shahid Hemmat Industrial Group (SHIG) and the Shahid\nBakeri Industrial Group (SBIG), both of which were designated in resolution 1737 (2006).\n[Old Reference # E.29.I.8]",
